item.description: Krishna Karthik is a passionate technologist who is currently purssuing Masters degree in Computer Science from NYU, Couranta. He did his undergraduate in Computer Science from the Indian Institute of Technology (IIT), Kanpur. After his bachelors he joined VMware as a software engineer, where he developed SaaS applicaitons and contributed to open source projects. Karthik is one of the major contributors and maintainer for open source project Purser.
